ion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00000=
0; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> a few years ago</a=
>, you can get lots of press releases early and trade on them and make mone=
y.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you=C2=A0<em>work=C2=A0</em>at a news=
wire then I guess you can also do that, but you are more likely to get caug=
ht? Here is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/273432=
