</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you do some crime and get a lot of =
Bitcoins for it, and the authorities want to seize your Bitcoins, can they?=
 There is a <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/273432=
69.270594/aHR0cHM6Ly94a2NkLmNvbS81Mzgv/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB3cc9eda9" i=
